BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:event_313637947@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260312T160923Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260409T170000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260409T200000
SUMMARY:**READ 1ST SENTENCE** GitHub Copilot Dev Days | Portland(-ish)\, Oregon
DESCRIPTION:PADNUG\n**\\*\\*Very Important!!!\\*\\*: This information is on here to quickly inform everyone. To actual register for the event\, however\, you must visit this site: [GitHub Copilot Dev Days | Portland\, OR · Luma](https://luma.com/x5fwhl5u?tk=6O6AC0)**\n\n(*This is why the attendee count is zero!*)\n\nJoin us for a community-led developer event focused on **AI-assisted coding with GitHub Copilot**. This event brings together developers to explore practical workflows\, real-world use cases\, and hands-on experiences using GitHub Copilot.\n\n​Whether you are new to GitHub Copilot or already using it\, this event will help you better understand how to apply AI-assisted coding techniques in everyday development.\n\n## ​**📅 Agenda**\n\n​*5:00 PM* – **Check-in & Pizza 🍕**\n​*5:30 PM* – **Welcome & Opening with James Montemagno and Scott Hanselman**\n​*5:30 PM* – **Session 1: GitHub Copilot: Your AI Companion for Every Workflow**\n​*6:00 PM* – **Session 2: Deep Dive into the GitHub Copilot CLI**\n​*6:30 PM* – **Workshop: Hands-on with GitHub Copilot**\n​*8:00 PM* – **Closing & Next Steps**
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/padnug/events/313637947/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260304T203719Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260304T203719Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/d/a/9/a/600_533035962.jpeg
END:VEVENT
